00:30:31.400 --> 00:30:37.280
The film-- giving you
a very raw deal here.

00:30:37.280 --> 00:30:41.210
And I talked about just
the hydro component of it.

00:30:41.210 --> 00:30:44.830
And hydro is just
1/3 of the film.

00:30:44.830 --> 00:30:45.580
There's coal.

00:30:45.580 --> 00:30:47.840
And then there's the
rise of solar and wind.

00:30:47.840 --> 00:30:50.230
And we go in depth
into each area,

00:30:50.230 --> 00:30:52.990
talking to-- again--
researchers, doctors,

00:30:52.990 --> 00:30:57.670
