00:38:12.630 --> 00:38:15.220
But then please be
mindful that it's just

00:38:15.220 --> 00:38:17.317
the tip of the iceberg
of what actually

00:38:17.317 --> 00:38:19.650
is happening all over the
country and all over the world

00:38:19.650 --> 00:38:21.150
probably.

00:38:21.150 --> 00:38:23.590
