arguments put forth.

00:38:23.590 --> 00:38:28.650
But when you compare
just what a dam does

00:38:28.650 --> 00:38:34.410
to a river and the ecosystem and
what a distributed solar model

00:38:34.410 --> 00:38:40.680
does, there is no
comparison, when

00:38:40.680 --> 00:38:42.780
it comes to
destroying livelihoods

00:38:42.780 --> 00:38:48.234
and cultures and just the
ecology of the entire region.

